  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的继承关系图。核心想法是：租户层有两个关键组件，遥测流和控制器，它们都继承自库层的基础实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "tenant",
        "library"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以租户层是实际部署的实例，库层是底层基础组件。库层除了遥测流，还有哪些基础组件需要放进来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenant",
        "library"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "库层需要三个：遥测流、PLC逻辑、边缘节点。控制器的继承关系比较特殊——它继承自PLC逻辑，而不是遥测流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先搭建整体结构。左右布局，左边租户子图放遥测流和控制器，右边库子图放三个基础组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenant",
        "library",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "继承关系我这样画：租户遥测流指向库遥测流，控制器指向PLC逻辑。关系标签用\"inherits from\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inherits",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，标签用\"inherits from\"准确。不过要注意租户和库里都有遥测流，名字一样但层级不同，别连错了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "tenant",
        "library"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。租户遥测流A继承自库遥测流C，控制器B继承自PLC逻辑D。边缘节点E暂时没有继承关系，作为库层独立组件存在。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "inherits"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "边缘节点的设计是对的，它目前是基础能力，租户层还没用到。不过我想确认一下方向——继承箭头是从子类指向父类对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inherits",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，箭头从租户组件出发，指向库组件，表示依赖和继承来源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inherits"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才看错了。租户遥测流和库遥测流虽然名字相同，但必须是两个独立节点，不能合并。你画的是分开的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "tenant",
        "library"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认是分开的，租户里标为A，库里标为C，两个独立矩形。继承线连接A到C，不会混淆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "tenant",
        "library"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了。这个结构清晰展示了租户层如何复用和扩展库层能力，边缘节点预留了扩展空间。可以定稿。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tenant",
        "library",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
